Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:58.56,cn-ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}也照耀著我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.36,cn-ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}同樣的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:08.28,cn-ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}一定是為了將歸途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:17.29,cn-ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}照亮的小小的希望
